@10702  = ~~
@10705  = ~Lord Entar! You must come quickly! Oh, hello everyone...~
@10706  = ~Wait - what is <CHARNAME> doing here?? I just saw you...~
@10707  = ~Calm down, man. Tell us what news is so urgent, and what is confusing you.~ // belt
@10708  = ~Alright, sir. I rushed here to find Lord Entar, to tell you that someone has confessed to the attack on your person, that, um, killed you. Temporarily, I suppose. But still.~
@10709  = ~What are you talking about? Who made that confession? Where is this person now? Out with it, man!~ // entar
@10710  = ~Well, that's the thing, sir. It... well, it is <CHARNAME>. Walked right into Headquarters, said something about the scheme being undone with Sarevok dead, and <PRO_HESHE> wanted to repent. I put <PRO_HIMHER> into a cell, and came straight here to inform you. Only, now I see <CHARNAME> before me... but how? That cell is warded against magical escape!~
@10711  = ~<CHARNAME> has been here with us for some time now. And came here after reportedly dispatching Sarevok <PRO_HIMHER>self.~ // belt
@10712  = ~If we are to trust that report!~ // entar
@10713  = ~Entar, I know you are upset, and not without reason. But better to solve this mystery and know the truth. I suggest we all go to the Flaming Fist headquarters and see for ourselves.~ // liia
@10714  = ~Agreed. <CHARNAME>, you will accompany us. It would be in your own best interest to clear this up.~ // belt
@10715  = ~Very well, we will travel there together.~ // cut1
@10716  = ~With all due respect, you can see plainly that I am here in front of you and not at the Flaming Fist Headquarters. This is an undue imposition on my time and person.~
@10717  = ~I think not. I have had enough of your orders and mistrust. I have better things to do than stay here.~
@10718  = ~<CHARNAME>, this is not a request. We are the lords of the city and we are ordering you to travel in our custody to determine what has happened here. Refuse to do this voluntarily, and we will have no choice but to use force.~ // belt
@10719  = ~Very well, I do not want to make enemies of the whole city. I will accompany you and see this sorted out.~ // cut
@10720  = ~I said I had enough and I meant I had enough! I am leaving now, whether you allow it our not!~ // fight
